William Jones, Plaintiff in Error, v. J. R. Tyler, Defendant in Error. Frazier and Mabry, for Plaintiff in Error. Circuit Court of Hillsborough County; J. B. Wall, Judge. August 10, 1909.

Writ of error from a judgment in favor of the defendant in error. Dismissed before the clerk on praecipe of counsel for plaintiff in error,
